OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FChance of a
OL,6,Ffew showers at first this evening
OL,7,Fotherwise dry. Thickening cloud will
OL,8,Fbring some patchy rain from the west
OL,9,Ffor a time in the early hours. Chance
OL,10,Fof a slight frost in the north.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA dry start but some patchy
OL,13,Frain later in the morning and early
OL,14,Fafternoon. Otherwise dry and rather
OL,15,Fcloudy. Freshening southerly winds
OL,16,Falong the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
